<script>
  	async function logLastChat() {
        const chatWindow = document.getElementById('chat-window-messages');
        if (chatWindow) {
            const chatRightMessages = document.querySelectorAll('.chat-right .chat-content');
            const lastChatRightMessage = chatRightMessages[chatRightMessages.length - 1];
            if (lastChatRightMessage) {
                const messageContent = lastChatRightMessage.textContent.trim();
                if (messageContent) {
                    const referrer = document.referrer;

                    let urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
                    let paramsObject = {};
                    const utmParams = {};

                    const utmKeys = ['utm_source', 'utm_medium', 'utm_campaign', 'utm_term', 'utm_content'];

                    urlParams.forEach((value, key) => {
                        paramsObject[key] = value;
                        document.cookie = key + "=" + value;
                    });
                    const urlParamsString = JSON.stringify(paramsObject);

                    utmKeys.forEach(key => {
                        if (urlParams.has(key)) {
                            utmParams[key] = urlParams.get(key);
                        }
                    });

                    const cookie = document.cookie;

                    const url = 'https://contao.ra-cocron.de/jupus/chatbot/log';
                    const data = {
                        message: messageContent,
                        referrer: referrer,
                        url_parameters: urlParamsString,
                        cookie: cookie,
                        is_last: true,
                    };

                    // Add UTM parameters to the data object
                    for (const key in utmParams) {
                        if (utmParams.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
                            data[key] = utmParams[key];
                        }
                    }

                    try {
                        const response = await fetch(url, {
                            method: 'POST',
                            headers: {
                                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                                'Referer': referrer,
                            },
                            body: JSON.stringify(data),
                        });

                        // Check if the request was successful
                        if (response.ok) {
                            // console.log('Message saved successfully:', message);
                        } else {
                            // console.error('Error saving message:', response.status);
                        }
                    } catch (error) {
                        // console.error('Error sending POST request:', error);
                    }
                }

            }
        }
    }
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        // Get the links
        const emailLink = document.getElementById("topbar-email");
        //const appointmentLink = document.getElementById("topbar-appointment");
        const berlinPhoneLink = document.getElementById("topbar-berlin-phone");
        const muenchenPhoneLink = document.getElementById("topbar-muenchen-phone");

        // Create event listeners for each link
        emailLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_email_click"
            });
        });

        {/* appointmentLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_appointment_click"
            });
        }); */}

        berlinPhoneLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_phone_berlin_click"
            });
        });

        muenchenPhoneLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_phone_muenchen_click"
            });
        });

        // Intercept dataLayer pushes
        (function () {
            const originalPush = dataLayer.push;
            dataLayer.push = function () {
                const args = Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments);
                let isBlocked = false;
                args.forEach(async function (obj) {
                    //console.log('marketing', BorlabsCookie.Consents.hasConsentForServiceGroup('marketing'));
                    // only when marketing consent true
                    if (BorlabsCookie.Consents.hasConsentForServiceGroup('marketing')!== true) {
                        if (obj && obj.event === 'topbar_email_click') {
                            //   gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //       'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/J-R9CIHPmIsbEOiSvZc_',
                            //       'value': 1.0,
                            //       'currency': 'EUR'
                            //   });
                            isBlocked = true;
                            console.log('topbar_email_click');
                        } else if (obj && obj.event === 'topbar_appointment_click') {
                            //   gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //       'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/C-lECLyKposbEOiSvZc_',
                            //       'value': 1.0,
                            //       'currency': 'EUR'
                            //   });
                            console.log('topbar_appointment_click');
                            isBlocked = true;
                        } else if (obj && obj.event === 'topbar_phone_berlin_click') {
                            //gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //    'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/0d5-CL-KposbEOiSvZc_',
                            //    'value': 1.0,
                            //    'currency': 'EUR'
                            //});
                            console.log('topbar_phone_berlin_click');
                            isBlocked = true;
                        } else if (obj && obj.event === 'topbar_phone_muenchen_click') {
                            //   gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //       'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/Bo8YCLqLposbEOiSvZc_',
                            //       'value': 1.0,
                            //       'currency': 'EUR'
                            //   });
                            console.log('topbar_phone_muenchen_click');
                            isBlocked = true;
                        } else if (obj && obj.event === 'cocron_chatbot_contact_attorney') {
                            //   gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //        'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/CI1fCKyrposbEOiSvZc_',
                            //        'value': 1.0,
                            //        'currency': 'EUR'
                            //   });
                            console.log('cocron_chatbot_contact_attorney');
                            isBlocked = true;
                        } else if (obj && obj.event === 'jupus_chat_completed') {
                            //   gtag('event', 'conversion', {
                            //        'send_to': 'AW-16960670056/c3UYCNm2posbEOiSvZc_',
                            //        'value': 1.0,
                            //        'currency': 'EUR'
                            //   });
                            console.log('jupus_chat_completed');
                            isBlocked = true;

<script>
  	async function logLastChat() {
        const chatWindow = document.getElementById('chat-window-messages');
        if (chatWindow) {
            const chatRightMessages = document.querySelectorAll('.chat-right .chat-content');
            const lastChatRightMessage = chatRightMessages[chatRightMessages.length - 1];
            if (lastChatRightMessage) {
                const messageContent = lastChatRightMessage.textContent.trim();
                if (messageContent) {
                    const referrer = document.referrer;

                    let urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
                    let paramsObject = {};
                    const utmParams = {};

                    const utmKeys = ['utm_source', 'utm_medium', 'utm_campaign', 'utm_term', 'utm_content'];

                    urlParams.forEach((value, key) => {
                        paramsObject[key] = value;
                        document.cookie = key + "=" + value;
                    });
                    const urlParamsString = JSON.stringify(paramsObject);

                    utmKeys.forEach(key => {
                        if (urlParams.has(key)) {
                            utmParams[key] = urlParams.get(key);
                        }
                    });

                    const cookie = document.cookie;

                    const url = 'https://contao.ra-cocron.de/jupus/chatbot/log';
                    const data = {
                        message: messageContent,
                        referrer: referrer,
                        url_parameters: urlParamsString,
                        cookie: cookie,
                        is_last: true,
                    };

                    // Add UTM parameters to the data object
                    for (const key in utmParams) {
                        if (utmParams.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
                            data[key] = utmParams[key];
                        }
                    }

                    try {
                        const response = await fetch(url, {
                            method: 'POST',
                            headers: {
                                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                                'Referer': referrer,
                            },
                            body: JSON.stringify(data),
                        });

                        // Check if the request was successful
                        if (response.ok) {
                            // console.log('Message saved successfully:', message);
                        } else {
                            // console.error('Error saving message:', response.status);
                        }
                    } catch (error) {
                        // console.error('Error sending POST request:', error);
                    }
                }

            }
        }
    }

  window.addEventListener("resize", setUlMargin);

  function setUlMargin() {
    const header = document.querySelector("header");
    const ul = document.querySelector(".cr-header__nav-items");

    if (header && ul && window.innerWidth <= 768) {
      const headerHeight = header.offsetHeight;
      ul.style.top = "0";
      ul.style.marginTop = `${headerHeight}px`;
    }
  }
